item.title: CVE-2022-2554|2024-08-03T00:39:08.043Z -- unknown -- enable%20media%20replace
item.description: The Enable Media Replace WordPress plugin before 4.0.0 does not ensure that renamed files are moved to the Upload folder, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to move them outside to the web root directory via a path traversal attack for example
